feeder routes , marked by dotted lines , will run around the city bowl suburbs , from the end of sea point to camps bay and on to hout bay , and from camps bay over kloof nek to town .
on the west coast , the feeder services will run around table view and parklands , to bloubergstrand and atlantis , including the atlantis industrial area and saxonsea , and to mamre .
